{
  "description": "A picturesque view of a harbor or port at either sunrise or sunset. Multiple large, industrial gantry cranes dominate the foreground, silhouetted against a vibrant, warm-colored sky. The sky transitions from a brilliant orange near the horizon to a softer peach and pink higher up.  The cranes are positioned along a long concrete pier. Reflections of the cranes and the sky shimmer on the calm water of the harbor.  A row of parked vehicles, possibly trucks or delivery vans, are visible on the pier behind the cranes. Distant structures, potentially buildings or more distant cranes, are faintly visible in the background.  The scene evokes a sense of industry and the quiet beauty of a working waterfront.",
